-- Putin Says Arctic Continental Shelf Dispute Can Be Resolved by Negotiation
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2010-09-23T09:02:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/putin-says-arctic-continental-shelf-dispute-can-be-resolved-by-negotiation.html
Russian Prime Minister Vladimir
Putin said all current issues in the Arctic region, including
access to the continental shelf, can be resolved “in the spirit
of partnership.” He spoke to a conference in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
